{"tid":188370,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"做IT都發達？ Google前工程師10億人工","createTime":"2017-04-05T15:28:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-05T17:31:56.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e7f978ea312f2511e58c6ca6c989c49c3c8d91cd","tid":188370,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T15:28:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/financeestate/art/20170405/19980720\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Ffinanceestate%2Fart%2F20170405%2F19980720&d=Fzfx2iZ%2BI%2BdTugby0OFGQwCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=eb969419\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Ffinanceestate%2Fart%2F20170405%2F19980720&h=c816ceef\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/financeestate/art/20170405/19980720</a><br />\n<br />\n香港做IT人一向被批評冇前途，「宅男先做」，香港創新科技局成立以來，沒突出建樹，不過各位IT人及工程師切勿灰心，因為Google一位開發無人駕駛技術的工程師，人工就高達9.4億港元（約1.2億美元），恨死不少同行。<br />\n<br />\n事緣Google的無人駕駛子公司Waymo和Uber就一單無人駕駛技術官司正在審訊中，當中呈堂的人證及證物中，一位Google前工程師Anthony Levandowski的人工卻成為焦點，Anthony Levandowski為Google研究及開發無人駕駛技術時，所獲得的酬金高達1.2億美元，但其後Levandowski劈炮唔撈，自己成立研究無人駕駛的公司Otto，其後被Uber收購。<br />\n<br />\n案情指而Waymo控訴Levandowski從舊公司偷取大量無人駕駛技術的檔案及文件，要求法庭頒令，禁止Uber發展無人駕駛技術。"},{"pid":"992c6e6e362de1fc7fdae0e6e19d5d738e6b00c7","tid":188370,"uid":71710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T16:11:18.000Z","msg":"但萬中無一&hellip;<br />\n要睇都唔會睇依d極端例子"},{"pid":"dd9b758663dd3b09674fdef93bf325bc8e4ccfce","tid":188370,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T16:38:03.000Z","msg":"IT狗最鐘薏搵外國來打J<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e71d9aebdc2d53d163d93231933958977b737033","tid":188370,"uid":34955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T17:13:14.000Z","msg":"人地外國IT人見到人工低識reject offer識跳槽走人<br />\n香港班IT狗咩狗屎垃圾無限OT offer都照要<br />\n我係香港老闆都唔會俾面你班IT狗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/